rows.label: tlk45420144_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Vandham always manages to find
the most interesting individuals
to bring back here, doesn't he?

rows.label: tlk45420144_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I never thought the legendary Holy Grail
would be such a cute girl! I mean, not
that that's a bad thing or anything.

rows.label: tlk45420144_01_msg0003
rows.name:
But yeah, we take all sorts here.
When you've seen as many crazy folk
as we have, Holy Grail is no biggie.
